title: Salute Of The Jugger DivX
description: In the tradition of 'Mad Max' and 'Gladiator' comes this futuristic action adventure where heroes fight for glory and survival. Sallow (Rugter Hauer) is the hardened, bitter leader of this small band of heroes, and he is joined by Kidda (Joan Chen) whose reckless ambition to be the best Jugger team inspires Sallow into fighting to join 'The League'.
